N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 345.3 - Notification to applicant of nonapproval

State Regulations

Upon refusal to recommend approval of an application for
authority to practice, the Chiropractic Practice Committee shall notify the
applicant, in writing, of such refusal. Notes
